column5: I am not claiming to be the father of Anna Nicole Smith's baby and will gladly take a paternity test to prove it.  Does this place me in a minority?
That's how they all start Connie...denial!  Not sure why anyone would actually admit they went near that....
From the sound of it, paternity isn't the only thing they should be getting tested for!
Neither am I TG... but I refuse to take a paternity test!!!
If you check the log book you will see my name is NOT listed,. so it was not me
TG,I think your hiding something  Dont you invest in oil ?  Wasn't Anna married to an Oil Tycoon  Let me guess,your blood line is along those of Eric The Great
LOL me either, no part of that for me!
I just got my court order yesterday. Damm tequila.
Just heard in the news " no voluteers for Homolka's boy"   Any takers   :thumbsup_anim:
ACK!!!!!!!!  Take the kid away from her!!!!
Classic!

i dont know about a Jumla..??? but unfortunataly Homolka is a person... and a  dirtbag of one at that... Responsable for several particularily unpleasant murders, one extremely close to my own home, and got off with little punishment because she brought forth evidence locking up Bernardo... that was before they got more evidence proving she was a major player in the horrific crime...

The worst part is they were all (if i am not mistaken) female and in their early teens... Sicko's who should have something worse than just being put in jail... maybe some hard labour, and the hourly pineapple up the... Cant believe people can be so hateful and disgusting.
Please, please, please  . I was only jocking for a moment (my bad   ). Do not waste any more pixels on this person (or should I say piece of  s***t)
